# {{.Type}}: {{.Name}}

`{{.Name}}` provides a resource for managing OpenTelemetry metric integrations at the project level. This resource allows you to push Atlas metrics to any OTLP-compatible endpoint such as Datadog, New Relic, or Dynatrace.

To use this resource, the requesting Service Account or API Key must have the Organization Owner or Project Owner role.

~> **Note:** After importing this resource, the `headers` attribute will show a diff on the first plan because the Atlas API redacts header values in GET responses. Run `terraform apply` once to reconcile the state.

